iv><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;">Thank you for giving us the opportunity to assist you.</div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" size="3"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Regards,</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Case.OwnerFullName} | Customer Service Representative</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Global Business and Finance Services | office 1-800-786-7693 (SUNPOWER) |</font></div></div>]]></td>
